{"lastModified":1770205615680,"uri":"c::8344947358::vessel::d5cc4f43-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\n'Gorgeous', built in 2004 and last refitted in 2021/2022, is an elegant Canados 72'. She presents a comfortable leather salon with earthy colors and a cozy dining area on the Main deck. She accommodates up to ten guests in four spacious en-suite cabins - one Master with walk-in wardrobe, one VIP, one comfortable cabin with a semi-double bed plus a pullman berth and one twin cabin with a pullman berth as well. Her aft deck is fitted with a large raised table surrounded by chairs and an integrated sofa for alfresco dining. The Main deck connects around to the foredeck, where a spacious sun pad is laid out across the bow for uninterrupted views and sunlight. On the sundeck guests will enjoy casual alfresco dining and sunbathing at the two sun pads placed on the foredeck. Gorgeous offers a wide variety of new water toys!\nHer professional crew of three will guarantee an excellent charter experience and will pamper the guests throughout their vacations!","blueprint":{"name":"GORGEOUS","images":["/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cc4f43-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::79c277d0-a036-11ee-a7ac-d7be8742705d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cc4f43-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::79c3fe70-a036-11ee-a7ac-d7be8742705d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cc4f43-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::79c473a0-a036-11ee-a7ac-d7be8742705d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cc4f43-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::79c4e8d0-a036-11ee-a7ac-d7be8742705d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cc4f43-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::830f9a20-a036-11ee-a7ac-d7be8742705d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cc4f43-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets